'''小彌爾頓·豪艾里'''（{{lang-en|Milton Howery Jr.}}，{{bd|1979年|12月17日}}）<ref name="attack">{{Cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2009-06-15-0906150100-story.html|title=Chicago Laugh Attack|last=Vivanco|first=Leonor|date=2009-06-15|website=chicagotribune.com|access-date=2018-12-30|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411082534/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2009-06-15-0906150100-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>或稱為'''李利·萊爾·豪艾里'''（{{lang-en|Lil Rel Howery}}），是一名[[美國|美國]]男演員和喜劇演員。知名於[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]電視情景喜劇《{{le|傑洛向前衝|The Carmichael Show}}》（2015年至2017年）中的羅伯·卡麥克爾（{{lang|en|Robert Carmichael}}），以及電影《[[逃出絕命鎮|逃出絕命鎮]]》（2017年）中的[[運輸安全管理局|TSA]]官員羅德·威廉斯（{{lang|en|Rod Williams}}）一角。他還創作和製片、主演電視劇《{{le|雷爾 (電視劇)|Rel (TV series)|雷爾}}》（2018年至2019年）。

== 個人生活 ==
豪艾里於2008年11月24日與維琳娜·羅賓遜（{{lang|en|Verina Robinson}}）結婚<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2018/09/07/lil-rel-howerys-life-is-now-a-sitcom/|title=Lil Rel Howery's life is now a sitcom|last=Jones|first=Tashara|date=2018-09-07|website=New York Post|language=en|access-date=2018-12-30|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109023554/https://nypost.com/2018/09/07/lil-rel-howerys-life-is-now-a-sitcom/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="drama">{{Cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-ent-lil-rel-howery-sitcom-20180906-story.html|title=Lil Rel Howery's TV career is about to take off as he deals with real-life Chicago drama|last=Swartz|first=Tracy|date=2018-09-06|website=chicagotribune.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-30|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025645/https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/tv/ct-ent-lil-rel-howery-sitcom-20180906-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們育有兩個孩子。夫妻倆於2017年離婚<ref name= drama/><ref>Bocque, Anslem Samuel (March 2, 2018). "[https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2018/03/comedian-lil-rel-howery-on-landing-get-out-role-and-now-starring-in-uncle-drew From 'Get Out' to Balling With Kyrie Irving, Lil Rel Howery Isn't Done Having the Best Year Ever] {{Wayback|url=https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2018/03/comedian-lil-rel-howery-on-landing-get-out-role-and-now-starring-in-uncle-drew |date=20200919072318 }}. ''Complex''. Retrieved 2018-09-22.</ref>。

2016年6月，豪艾里的車子在{{le|小義大利 (芝加哥)|Little Italy, Chicago|芝加哥大學村}}撞上另一輛車<ref name="arrested">{{Cite web|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/chicago-comedian-lil-rel-howery-arrested-on-near-west-side/|title=Chicago comedian Lil Rel Howery arrested on Near West Side|last=Owen|first=Jordan|date=2016-06-20|website=Chicago Sun-Times|language=en|access-date=2018-12-30|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411082653/https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/chicago-comedian-lil-rel-howery-arrested-on-near-west-side/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一輛車上的駕駛員與他發生爭吵，並最終致電[[911_(求救電話)|911]]。據稱，豪艾里出手攻擊了對方的臉。<ref name=arrested/><ref name= celeb>"Celebrity File". ''Daily Post'' (Palo Alto, California). 2016-06-21. p. 26.</ref>豪艾里車上的駕駛自行[[肇事逃逸|肇事逃逸]]<ref name= arrested/>。警察到達並以{{le|毆擊罪|Battery (crime)|輕度毆擊罪}}拘捕了豪艾里，事後被判無罪。該名駕駛狀告豪艾里出手使自己受傷。<ref name= drama/>

